{"word":"H540 - אֲמַן - ʼăman - am-an' - Believe","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲמַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼăman"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>am-an'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"விசுவாசி, சத்தியமாயிரு. உண்மையுள்ளவனாயிரு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to confirm, to support (Aphel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to believe in"},{"paragraph":"2) to trust"},{"paragraph":"3) trustworthy (passive participle)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); corresponding to <a href=\"#/H539 - אָמַן - ʼâman - aw-man'/539\">H539</a>: - believe, faithful, sure."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}